c: 2
v: 135
t: "(Abayahudi babwira abakurikiye intumwa Muhamadi) baravuze bati \"Nimube Abayahudi ni bwo muzayoboka;nAbakirisitu (babwira abakurikiye intumwa Muhamadi) bati \"Mube Abakirisitu ni bwo muzayoboka\". Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ahubwo (ukuyoboka nyako ni ugukurikira) idini ritunganye rya Ibrahim (ritabangikanya Allah). Kandi ntiyari mu babangikanyamana"